headline: Is Humana Offering Long Term Value After a 50% Slide and DCF Rebound?
summary: Wondering if Humana is quietly turning into a value opportunity after a rough stretch, or if the stock is cheap for a reason? Let us break down what the current share price is really telling us. After a tough multi year slide, with the stock still down 50.1% over 3 years and 31.1% over 5 years, Humana has shown signs of life recently, gaining 4.9% over the last week and 2.1% year to date.
